channel.title: Can i please get a couple testers
channel.description:
ive been working on this chat room for ages, i psoted this once b4, i need testers for it. it owuld be a nice replacement for the yell command on private servers as its small and doesnt use much memory, but idk if there are any holes because its on my pc, i need to know if everything works remotely, and i need to knwo if others find it easy to understand. to sign in just do one of the folowing 1. click start/run, type in telnet 1mixscape1.servegame.com 2. type in telnet and then type o 1mixscape1.servegame.com 3 make a batch file that sais @echo off telnet 1mixscape1.servegame.com
ty for anyone who helps test it.
